title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 §§ 753-4.2 - Removal of underground facilities
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 §§ 753-4.2 - Removal of underground facilities

State Regulations

Any operator who removes or transfers ownership of all of
his or her underground facilities from within the boundaries of any one-call
notification system shall promptly notify the system. Notes
